	<h1>About Our Club</h1>
	<h2>Welcome to the Movies and Dramatics Club of SRM University!</h2>
	<p>
		Our club is a vibrant community dedicated to celebrating various aspects of
		the performing arts. We collaborate with young entertainers and provide a
		dynamic platform for students passionate about the thespian world.
	</p>
	<h2>Our Mission</h2>
	<p>
		At the Movies and Dramatics Club, our mission is to:
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Discover and nurture the innate artistic talents among our students.</li>
		<li>Provide opportunities for talented individuals to showcase their skills
			and creativity.</li>
		<li>Foster the development of essential skills such as communication,
			teamwork, dialogue, and socialization through the performing arts.</li>
	</ul>
	<h2>Our History</h2>
	<p>
		Founded in 2014, the Movies and Dramatics Club has grown from a small group
		of enthusiasts to a cornerstone of campus life at SRM University. Over the
		years, we have staged numerous successful productions, hosted workshops with
		industry professionals, and built a strong community of passionate
		performers and creators.
	</p>
	<h2>Our Team</h2>
	<p>
		Our club is led by a dedicated team of convenors who bring a wealth of
		experience and enthusiasm to our activities. Meet our team:
	</p>
